text: Bùi Tiến Dụng (born 23 November 1998) is a Vietnamese footballer who plays as a central midfielder for V-League (Vietnam) club SHB Đà Nẵng ==Honours== ===Club=== Than Quảng Ninh *Vietnamese Cup : Winners: : 2016 *Vietnamese Super Cup : Winners: : 2016 ===International=== Vietnam U19 *AFC U-19 Championship : Third place: : 2016 *AFF U-19 Youth Championship : Third place: : 2016 Vietnam U23 *AFC U-23 Championship : Runners-up : : 2018 *M-150 Cup : Third place: : 2017 == References == Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Vietnamese footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:V.League 1 players Category:Than Quảng Ninh F.C. players Category:People from Thanh Hóa Province Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games Category:Southeast Asian Games medalists in football Category:Southeast Asian Games gold medalists for Vietnam
title: Bùi Tiến Dụng
